! Simple use
The filter contains a list of tiddlers and list widget simplate iterates over them.

```
<ul>
<$list filter="[[Tiddler-A]] [[Tiddler-B]] [[Tiddler-C]]">
<li><<currentTiddler>></li>
</$list>
</ul>
